BooK was happy to see the presentation software I used, so here it is for
public use and tinkering.

$ ./make-presentation

Some CPAN modules are required, as well as Inkscape and pdftk. If you're on a
Mac, you'll have to do something about the hard-coded Inkscape path at the end
of the script.

The slides-making script is licensed under the Artistic License 2.0:
    <http://www.opensource.org/licenses/artistic-license-2.0.php>
